[normal]Written evidence from N[bold]orfolk County Council [bold](WRT 025)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]The experiences of the winter 2009-10 did bring many challenges to the Authority and certainly refinements have been made since.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Many adopted from both the 
[normal]Government report into winter resilience (
[normal]Quarmby
[normal]) and research by NWSRG (National Salt Spreading Research Group).
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]The impacts of salt supply shortages were minimised with the salt supply PFI in place.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Resilience further increased from the summer 2010 wi
[normal]th the introduction of a strategic stock.
[normal]&#xa0;
